<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/app.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Special+Gothic+Expanded+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logofinal.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/locomotive-scroll@4.1.4/dist/locomotive-scroll.min.css">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/locomotive-scroll@4.1.4/dist/locomotive-scroll.min.js"></script>
  <title>pizza.co</title>

  <style>
        html {
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        body {
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 2.5s forwards;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            padding-top: 80px;
        }
        [data-scroll-container] {
            perspective: 1px;
        }

        .project-title {
            font-size: 70px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            font-family: 'Special Gothic Expanded One', Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-left: 10%;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);
            animation: slideInLeft 0.8s ease;
        }

        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .project-description {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-family: 'Special Gothic Expanded One', Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: left;
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-top: 30px;
            max-width: 80%;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.3s backwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .project-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-left: 10%;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.5s backwards;
        }

        .project-links a {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-family: 'Special Gothic Expanded One', Arial, sans-serif;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 200px;
        }

        .project-links .btn-primary {
            background-color: #ff0000;
            color: black;
            border: 2.5px solid #ff0000;
        }

        .project-links .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: black;
            color: #ff0000;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .project-links .btn-secondary {
            border: 2.5px solid #ff0000;
            color: #ff0000;
        }

        .project-links .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #ff0000;
            color: black;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.8);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .project-image {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            max-width: 80%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: block;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.7s backwards;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .project-image:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .back-button {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease 0.9s backwards;
        }

        .btn-outline-light:hover {
            transform: translateX(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body data-scroll-container>
    <%- include('partials/header', { activePage: 'portfolio' }) %>
    <%- include('partials/videobg') %>

    <div class="container-fluid" data-scroll-section>
        <h1 class="project-title">pizza.co</h1>
        
        <div class="project-description">
            so basically, i created this react app where people can build their own pizzas.<br>
            customize the toppings, sizes, crusts - you name it. real-time order summary,<br>
            mock checkout, the whole deal. it was a fun way to level up my react skills and<br>
            work with state management. check it out if you're hungry for some code. 
        </div>

        <div class="project-links">
            <a href="https://pizzaco-lime.vercel.app/" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">view live</a>
        </div>

        <img src="/pizzacoshowcase.png" alt="pizza.co project" class="project-image">

        <div class="back-button">
            <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-outline-light">back to portfolio</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const scroll = new LocomotiveScroll({
            el: document.querySelector('[data-scroll-container]'),
            smooth: true,
            smoothMobile: true,
            multiplier: 1.2,
            lerp: 0.075,
            reloadOnContextChange: true
        });

        window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
            scroll.update();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
